A million of these but it would mean a lot if there was anything you could do to help us reach our goal of feeding over $150 families and gifting to over 250 kids. 

Signed,

A woman who believes in her company mission.

Christmas we try to ensure that each child on our caseload who was not given a gift by the state receives a toy for Christmas. We call it UFC's season of giving. We are privately owned non for profit agency with 2 main locations on Chicago's south side. I know you get a pt. 2
